X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Description";ID=18998;TYPE=MultiLine:Se
 attle Fire Department&#39\;s Medic 2 Bystander CPR training Program is h
 osting a community CPR class at Seattle Fire Department Headquarters on 
 Tuesday\, April 7 from 5:30-8 p.m.<br><br>To register for the class plea
 se fill out this online form:&#160\;<a href="https://forms.office.com/pa
 ges/responsepage.aspx?id=RR7meOtrCUCPmTWdi1T0G9kwoVGUeZBNg-pNMdx4RydUMFV
