DESCRIPTION:Neighborhoods: Central Area/Squire Park<br>Event Types: Busi
 ness/Trade<br>Audience: Adults<br>Contact: Startup Valley<br>Contact Ema
 il: event@startupvalley.club<br>Pre-Register: Yes<br>Cost: 0<br>Link: ht
 tps://luma.com/9wwvlw59<br><br>&#8203\;Hi there!<br><br>&#8203\;&#x1F680
 \; Dear Participants! Join our event in Seattle!<br><br>&#8203\;Meet and
  network with Founders and Investors. Pitch to the audience with your St
 artup and seize your chance to dive into the world of business\, technol
 ogy\, and venture capital.<br><br>&#8203\;<br><br>&#8203\;&#x1F4A1\; Why
  You Can&#39\;t Miss This Event:<br><br>&#8203\;Engage with leading expe
 rts and founders in Tech &amp\; Business\, as well as top investors\, to
  gain deep insights and valuable networking.<br><br>&#8203\;This event i
 s essential for those looking to gain ideas\, experience\, and valuable 
 connections.<br><br>&#8203\;<br><br>&#8203\;&#x1F4C8\; Present Your Star
 tup in Tech &amp\; Business:<br><br>&#8203\;Showcase your startup in the
  Tech &amp\; Business fields! Send your pitch deck to <a href="mailto:co
 ntact.us@startupvalley.club" target="_blank" rel="noopener">contact.us@s
 tartupvalley.club</a> and seize the opportunity to impress both the audi
 ence and investors!<br><br>&#8203\;Also\, you need to fill out the appli
 cation to participate as a pitcher/speaker at the event.<br><br>&#8203\;
 Apply now!<br><br>&#8203\;<br><br>&#8203\;&#x1F4BC\; We Welcome New Inve
 stors:<br><br>&#8203\;We invite investors to our event to expand their n
 etwork\, get acquainted with new startups\, evaluate them\, provide feed
 back\, participate in discussions\, and gain access to a database of fre
 sh startups from around the world.<br><br>If you&#39\;d like access to a
  database of promising startup projects and additional benefits from Sta
 rtup Valley\, please fill out this application\, and our team will conta
 ct you.<br><br>&#8203\;Who you will meet at the event:<br><br>&#8203\;Fo
 unders<br><br>&#8203\;Investors or VC companies<br><br>&#8203\;Marketers
 \, Salespeople\, Business Advisers<br><br>&#8203\;Industry Disruptors<br
 ><br>&#8203\;AI Experts<br><br>&#8203\;Entrepreneurs from Europe\, Asia
 \, and the United Kingdom<br><br>&#8203\;<br><br>&#8203\;Requirements for
  attendees:<br><br>&#8203\;21+ years old<br><br>&#8203\;Neat appearance<
 br><br>&#8203\;Good mood<br><br>&#8203\;1 drink bought at the bar (non-a
 lcohol works too)<br><br>&#8203\;&#x1F91D\; The venue\, where we host ou
 r events\, is our partner. To continue hosting events at this location\,
  please consider purchasing 1-2 drinks at the bar. Thank you.<br><br>&#8
 203\;<br><br>&#8203\;Time:<br><br>&#8203\;Event time: 7:00 PM to 10:00 P
 M<br><br>&#8203\;Pitch time: 8:40 PM to 9:20 PM<br><br>&#8203\;<br><br>&
 #8203\;&#x1F39F\; Join our event and secure your ticket today! &#10024\;
 <br><br>&#8203\;Sincerely\,The Startup Valley Team<br><br>&#8203\;
