 e Market PDA<br>Contact: info@pikeplacemarket.org<br>Pre-Register: No<br
 >Cost: Free<br>Link: https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/gro
 w-and-gather-a-spring-gardening-festival/<br><br>Join us Saturday\, Apri
 l 18\, for a brand new event at Pike Place Market celebrating growers of
  all kinds. From the patio and backyard gardeners to the family farms th
 at sell at Pike Place Market and beyond. We invite gardeners and plant e
 nthusiasts to spend the afternoon at the Market supporting local farmers
  and learning more about growing and cooking with fresh produce. <br><br
 >Shop for locally grown produce\, fresh-cut flowers from our world-class
  farmers\, and learn about nonprofits that help the farming community ac
 ross the region. Full vendor lineup to come!<br><br>Bonus! Free Live Dem
 os: Get your gardening questions answered by Pacific Northwest legend Ci
 scoe Morris\, and learn how to cook with local seasonal ingredients from
  Chef Traci at the Atrium Kitchen.
