  Phone: 206-300-1268<br>Contact Email: gtoddyoung@gmail.com<br>Audience:
  Adults\,All\,Children\,Family\,Pets\,Senior\,Special Needs\,Teen<br>Pre
 -Register: No<br>Cost: Free<br><br><p>We meet at the Bath House Theater 
 parking lot on the NW corner of Green Lake Park every Sunday at 8:45 am 
 to sign in. All equipment provided.&#160\;<br><br>We walk the park every
  Sunday from 9:00am -11:00am. picking up as much litter as we can each w
 eek. All are welcome. Litter patrols happen rain or shine. Please dress 
 for the weather &amp\; 2+ mile walk.</p>
