DESCRIPTION:Event Description: Please join us for a wonderful story time
  event! Your local firefighters will lead this special story time for yo
 u and your friends. This will be fun-filled morning of storytelling and 
 learning about fire safety. Plus\, you will get a chance to meet your ne
 ighborhood firefighters and see a fire engine up close (if weather permi
 ts)! Families of all ages are welcome\, though this early learning progr
 am is intended for preschool ages and older (4+)\, their caregivers and 
 families.\n\nLearn more about Seattle Public Library Story Times here <a
  href="http://-https://www.spl.org/programs-and-services/fun-and-games/s
