  are here to help.<br> <br> The Pet Loss Support Group meets by phone/We
 bex every Thursday from 5:30-6:45 p.m. For the schedule and details on h
 ow to join the virtual meeting\, please email&#160\;<a href="mailto:sasp
 etloss@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">saspetloss@gmail.com</a
 >.<br> <br> <strong>PLEASE DO NOT SHOW UP AT SEATTLE ANIMAL SHELTER</str
 ong> - this meeting is only by phone/online\, not in person<br> <br> By 
 joining the meeting\, you confirm that you have read and agreed to the f
 ollowing City of Seattle&#8217\;s terms for participation:<br> The purpo
 se of the Pet Loss Support Group at the Seattle Animal Shelter is to pro
 vide short-term group support for individuals experiencing grief and gri
 ef-related issues due to the loss of a pet.<br> This program does not pr
 ovide professional counseling and/or assessment services for the treatme
 nt of psychological problems or disorders\, and participants will not be
  receiving professional therapeutic intervention through this program.<b
 r> As a condition of participating in this program\, I agree to release
 \, defend and indemnify the Seattle Animal Shelter\, the City of Seattle
 \, and their employees and volunteers from any loss or injury to my perso
 n and from all liability for any and all claims\, demands\, losses\, or 
 damages\, actions\, judgments of every kind and description arising out 
 of my participation in this program.
