 gency-management/community-engagement/stop-the-bleed<br><br>Life-threate
 ning bleeding injuries can happen anytime. When they do\, <strong>every 
 minute counts! </strong><br>&quot\;Stop the Bleed&quot\; empowers the pu
 blic to take action! Our trained instructors teach the community about b
 leeding control: recognizing life-threatening bleeding\, applying pressu
 re to the wound\, and using a tourniquet.
