DESCRIPTION:Venue: Seattle Fire Department Headquarters<br>Address: 301 
 2nd Ave S\nSeattle\, WA 98104<br>Event Description: Seattle Fire Departm
 ent&#39\;s Medic 2 Bystander CPR training Program is hosting a community
