 through the YMCA&#39\;s &quot\;Get Engaged&quot\; program.<br><br><stron
 g>Mission</strong><br>The Seattle Arts Commission supports the City by a
 dvocating for arts policy\, creating access for equitable participation 
 in the arts\, and fostering enriching arts engagement for all residents.
 
