  wall to reveal their flaws and journeys to redemption. The audience pla
 ys a vital part in The Circus of Second Chances\, in which ropes are dan
 cescapes\, trapezes are windows to the soul\, and spinning hoops are por
 tals to infinite possibility. In our homes we are out at sea\, on our li
 ving room couch we find ourselves on an epic odyssey\; so much rests upo
 n the fate of a dozen lemons. Leveraging their long running friendships 
 with each other\, Emma Curtiss\, Melissa Knowles\, and Terry Crane put a
 ll their talents and quirky craftiness into this dada circus romp. They 
 climb\, cavort\, invert\, revert\, and subvert in this capricious acroba
 tic piece as they ask\, &#8220\;What does your heart wish for?&#8221\;Ap
 propriate for all ages. 90 minutes\, no intermission.Featuring rope acro
 batics\, Cyr wheel\, handbalancing\, slack rope\, live baking\, and clow
 n. Performers: Emma Curtiss\, Melissa Knowles\, and Terry Crane. Music w
